flowchart TD
    A([Change Request]) --> A1[/"📋 Documentation Gate 1:\nBusiness Justification & Risk Assessment"/]
    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Documentation Gate 1
    A1 --> A2{Documentation\nComplete?}
    A2 --> |No| A1
    A2 --> |Yes| B{Emergency?}
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

    B --> |Yes| C[Emergency CAB]
    B --> |No| D[Standard Review]

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - SOX Compliance Check 1
    C --> C1{{"🔒 SOX Control:\nSegregation of Duties Check\n(Role: Compliance Officer)"}}
    C1 --> |Pass| E[Expedited Approval]
    C1 --> |Fail| C2[Remediate SoD Conflict\n👤 Role: Change Manager]
    C2 --> C1
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

    D --> F[Weekly CAB Meeting\n👤 Role: CAB Chair - Accountable]

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Documentation Gate 2
    F --> F1[/"📋 Documentation Gate 2:\nImpact Analysis & Test Evidence"/]
    F1 --> F2{Documentation\nComplete?}
    F2 --> |No| F1
    F2 --> |Yes| G{Approved?\n👤 Role: CAB Members - Responsible}
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

    G --> |Yes| G1{{"🔒 SOX Control:\nApproval Authorization Check\n(Role: Compliance Officer)"}}
    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - SOX Compliance Check 2
    G1 --> |Pass| H[Schedule Change Window\n👤 Role: Change Manager - Accountable]
    G1 --> |Fail| G2[Obtain Proper Authorization\n👤 Role: Change Owner]
    G2 --> G1
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

    G --> |No| I[Return to Requester\n👤 Role: Change Manager - Informed]

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Documentation Gate 3
    H --> H1[/"📋 Documentation Gate 3:\nImplementation Plan & Backout Plan"/]
    H1 --> H2{Documentation\nComplete?}
    H2 --> |No| H1
    H2 --> |Yes| J[Implementation\n👤 Role: Technical Team - Responsible\n👤 Role: Change Owner - Accountable]
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

    J --> K{Successful?}
    K --> |Yes| L[Post-Impl Review\n👤 Role: Change Manager - Responsible]

    K --> |No| M1[Execute Backout Plan\n👤 Role: Technical Team - Responsible]
    M1 --> M2{Backout Successful?}
    M2 --> |Yes| M3[Incident Report\n👤 Role: Change Owner - Accountable]
    M2 --> |No| M4[Escalate to Emergency CAB\n👤 Role: CAB Chair - Accountable]
    M4 --> M3

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - SOX Compliance Check 3 & Final Documentation Gate
    L --> L1{{"🔒 SOX Control:\nChange Evidence & Audit Trail Review\n(Role: Compliance Officer)"}}
    L1 --> |Pass| L2[/"📋 Documentation Gate 4:\nPost-Implementation Evidence Package"/]
    L1 --> |Fail| L3[Remediate Audit Findings\n👤 Role: Change Owner]
    L3 --> L1
    L2 --> N([Close Change\n👤 Role: Change Manager - Responsible\n👤 Role: Compliance Officer - Consulted])
    M3 --> L1
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

